# text: So to come back to the dilemma , if the dilemma is we have old-fashioned political nation-states unable to govern the world , respond to the global challenges that we face like climate change , then maybe it 's time for mayors to rule the world , for mayors and the citizens and the peoples they represent to engage in global governance .
